-the-international-cooperation-that-thwarted-the-iranian-attack-came-together/0000018e-e7a6-d7e3-a9bf-f7b709160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人和伊朗人似乎在一件事上达成了共识：我们谁都不想要这场战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-and-iranians-seem-to-agree-on-one-thing-none-of-us-want-this-war/0000018e-e739-db5b-afbe-ffbb39f50000</link><description>对我们来说不幸的是，伊朗和以色列的领导者将贪婪、骄傲和敌意置于人民之上——尽管两国开展了大规模抗议活动以结束这种情况</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:52:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-16/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-and-iranians-seem-to-agree-on-one-thing-none-of-us-want-this-war/0000018e-e739-db5b-afbe-ffbb39f50000</guid></item><item><title>“如果其中一枚导弹击中特拉维夫，我们将处于一个非常不同的、毁灭性的境地”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-16/ty-article-podcast/if-one-of-those-missiles-hit-tel-aviv-we-would-be-in-a-very-different-situation/0000018e-e6e6-dd85-abce-eef72da20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:47:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-16/ty-article-podcast/if-one-of-those-missiles-hit-tel-aviv-we-would-be-in-a-very-different-situation/0000018e-e6e6-dd85-abce-eef72da20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者破坏家园后，约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人重返废墟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/west-bank-village-residents-return-to-rubble-after-israeli-settlers-ravaged-their-homes/0000018e-e1e0-d9df-abdf-e7eb13970000</link><description>14 岁的本雅明·阿希米尔 (Binyamin Ahimeir) 的尸体被发现后，一群定居者突然袭击附近的一个村庄，放火焚烧汽车、房屋和其他财产。居民现在正试图收拾残局，表达了对旨在保护他们的当局缺乏信任：“我们甚至没有得到巴勒斯坦权力机构的保护”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:08:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/west-bank-village-residents-return-to-rubble-after-israeli-settlers-ravaged-their-homes/0000018e-e1e0-d9df-abdf-e7eb13970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 193 天：以色列国防军确认击毙真主党战地指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-193-idf-confirms-killing-hezbollah-field-commander/0000018e-e78d-d0ca-a99f-f7ffea480001</link><description>据报道，美国官员预计以色列对伊朗袭击的反应有限 ■ 美国、欧盟准备扩大对伊朗的制裁 ■ 以色列北部的三名以色列人被黎巴嫩发射的两架自杀式无人机炸伤 ■ 以色列消息来源：哈马斯最新的休战提议包括释放以色列境内不到 20 名人质第一阶段 ■ 以色列国防军确认真主党战地指挥官在黎巴嫩无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 战争开始 193 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:31:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-193-idf-confirms-killing-hezbollah-field-commander/0000018e-e78d-d0ca-a99f-f7ffea480001</guid></item><item><title>官方报告称，波兰前民族主义政府使用以色列制造的间谍软件针对数百人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-04-16/ty-article/polands-ex-nationalist-govt-used-israeli-made-spyware-on-hundreds-official-report-says/0000018e-e7aa-d0ca-a99f-f7fb64160000</link><description>波兰总检察长办公室的一份报告称，该国前政府使用以色列公司 NSO Group 制造的间谍软件 Pegasus 监控了近 600 人</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:28:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-04-16/ty-article/polands-ex-nationalist-govt-used-israeli-made-spyware-on-hundreds-official-report-says/0000018e-e7aa-d0ca-a99f-f7fb64160000</guid></item><item><title>作为以色列公民的加沙人没有一个国家可以将他们从地狱中拯救出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazans-who-are-also-israeli-citizens-dont-have-a-country-to-save-them-from-hell/0000018e-e6c5-de97-a5bf-f6f5981e0000</link><description>他们告别时说，他们的行李已经收拾好了，但军队改变的程序阻止了 47 名以色列人（其中一些是儿童）从加沙越过边境</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazans-who-are-also-israeli-citizens-dont-have-a-country-to-save-them-from-hell/0000018e-e6c5-de97-a5bf-f6f5981e0000</guid></item><item><title>新星节大屠杀的幸存者称以色列政府未能帮助他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/survivors-of-nova-festival-massacre-say-israeli-government-failing-to-help-them/0000018e-e777-dba7-a3ee-ff7f56da0000</link><description>遭受创伤的幸存者告诉议会委员会，他们在寻求帮助时遇到了不可接受的障碍，而一名官员证实，财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇正在搁置一项提供援助的内阁决议</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/survivors-of-nova-festival-massacre-say-israeli-government-failing-to-help-them/0000018e-e777-dba7-a3ee-ff7f56da0000</guid></item><item><title>法院下令将 35 名巴勒斯坦人驱逐出东耶路撒冷的房屋；财产将分配给以色列右翼团体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/courts-evict-35-palestinians-from-east-jerusalem-homes-for-israeli-right-wing-groups/0000018e-e707-db8e-a1bf-ff0f8a9f0000</link><description>法院裁定，巴勒斯坦家庭的房屋归一个右翼犹太团体所有，该团体获得了一家犹太信托公司的权益，该信托公司在 1948 年以色列建国之前购买了该地块。下令驱逐的以色列法官表示，他不会等待律师。将军的法律意见</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/courts-evict-35-palestinians-from-east-jerusalem-homes-for-israeli-right-wing-groups/0000018e-e707-db8e-a1bf-ff0f8a9f0000</guid></item><item><title>与伊朗有关的网站泄露以色列秘密数据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/click-here-for-sensitive-israeli-data-iran-linked-website-leaks-hacked-secret-info/0000018e-e6c8-de97-a5bf-f6f876a10000</link><description>自加沙战争以来针对以色列的网络攻击激增，一个新网站为反以色列黑客提供了一个平台，分享从以色列系统（包括国防部）窃取的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/click-here-for-sensitive-israeli-data-iran-linked-website-leaks-hacked-secret-info/0000018e-e6c8-de97-a5bf-f6f876a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列监狱将体育频道与右翼附属频道互换</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prisons-swap-sports-channel-with-right-wing-affiliated-channel/0000018e-e645-de89-afbf-ffe5ee980000</link><description>根据未向公众披露的新规定，刑事囚犯牢房中的电视现在必须播放所有四个新闻频道。 “为什么要在欧冠联赛之前剥夺一件给我们一点自由的东西呢？”一名囚犯说</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prisons-swap-sports-channel-with-right-wing-affiliated-channel/0000018e-e645-de89-afbf-ffe5ee980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列艺术家和策展人表示，在停火达成之前，威尼斯双年展以色列馆不会开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale-will-be-shut-until-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/0000018e-e5c6-d210-a7df-fdd6f9be0000</link><description>在要求将以色列排除在国际艺术活动之外和担心遭到破坏的呼声中，艺术家露丝·帕蒂尔和她的展览策展人呼吁加沙停火和释放人质协议，并表示“以色列馆将在这些条件成熟时开放”到达。&amp;#39;据报道，以色列政府并未获悉此次抗议活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale-will-be-shut-until-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/0000018e-e5c6-d210-a7df-fdd6f9be0000</guid></item><item><title>由于伊朗袭击后“持续的局势”，易捷航空暂停飞往以色列的航班直至十月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-oct-due-to-ongoing-situation-after-iran-attack/0000018e-e64e-de97-a5bf-f67e344f0000</link><description>该公司表示，由于以色列局势持续发展，易捷航空决定在夏季剩余时间内暂停飞往特拉维夫的航班，直至 10 月 27 日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-suspends-flights-to-israel-until-oct-due-to-ongoing-situation-after-iran-attack/0000018e-e64e-de97-a5bf-f67e344f0000</guid></item><item><title>为了对抗伊朗和哈马斯，以色列必须努力建立巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-confront-iran-and-hamas-israel-must-work-towards-a-palestinian-state/0000018e-e229-daaf-afaf-e7fd9b390000</link><description>加沙战争和伊朗袭击都清楚地表明以色列需要巴勒斯坦和地区伙伴。为了确保伊朗和哈马斯无法取得胜利，以色列必须停止拖延两国解决方案的进展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-confront-iran-and-hamas-israel-must-work-towards-a-palestinian-state/0000018e-e229-daaf-afaf-e7fd9b390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须权衡对伊朗针对真主党威胁发起的史无前例的袭击的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-weigh-response-to-irans-unprecedented-attack-against-the-threat-of-hezbollah/0000018e-e366-d071-a5be-e7e678700000</link><description>虽然伊朗的袭击需要以色列做出回应这一基本共识似乎跨越了政治界限，但官员们必须考虑到，如果局势进一步升级，伊朗可能会向其在黎巴嫩的代理人施压，要求其加入战争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-weigh-response-to-irans-unprecedented-attack-against-the-threat-of-hezbollah/0000018e-e366-d071-a5be-e7e678700000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗自身利益迫使其搁置与以色列的私人战争，缓和地区紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/iran-must-put-its-private-war-with-israel-to-one-side-and-lower-regional-tensions/0000018e-e3c2-daaf-afaf-e7f7501f0000</link><description>如果伊朗想要阻止中东联盟的形成来对抗它，它就必须保持与亲美阿拉伯邻国的关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article/.premium/iran-must-put-its-private-war-with-israel-to-one-side-and-lower-regional-tensions/0000018e-e3c2-daaf-afaf-e7f7501f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列战时内阁会议推迟，英国敦促内塔尼亚胡避免伊朗局势升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-live/idf-well-respond-to-iranian-missiles-iaea-worried-israel-could-hit-iran-nuclear-sites/0000018e-e478-de89-afbf-fffc831e0000</link><description>英国首相苏纳克告诉内塔尼亚胡中东局势升级不符合任何人的利益 ■ 博雷尔表示，欧盟将开始扩大对伊朗的制裁 ■ 克里姆林宫表示，伊朗告诉普京，它对局势升级不感兴趣 ■ 以色列北部无人机爆炸造成三人受伤 ■ 德国英国外交部长将抵达以色列，呼吁缓和与伊朗的紧张局势 ■ 以色列国防军记录：过去 24 小时内有 19 名士兵受伤，其中一名伤势严重</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-16/ty-article-live/idf-well-respond-to-iranian-missiles-iaea-worried-israel-could-hit-iran-nuclear-sites/0000018e-e478-de89-afbf-fffc831e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列回应高等法院：我们正在解决加沙地带人道主义援助问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israeך-responds-to-high-court-were-fixing-gaza-strip-humanitarian-aid-problems/0000018e-e31a-d08c-a5af-fb7b7a9d0000</link><description>在人权组织向以色列最高法院请愿增加进入加沙地带的援助物资数量后，以色列政府辩称哈马斯和抢劫事件正在扰乱援助物资的分配</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 19:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israeך-responds-to-high-court-were-fixing-gaza-strip-humanitarian-aid-problems/0000018e-e31a-d08c-a5af-fb7b7a9d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>